entities.description:
# Bootstrap DSP
![Bootstrap](https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/372475592/1592361111/1500x500)

Accelerate your development with Bootstrap DSP and Adobe XD for Visual Studio Code!

It's built from the [XD-Bootstrap-v.5-UI-Kit](https://assets.adobe.com/public/12e45de1-ef2f-4ec8-6b99-28b1012038a4) CC Library.

## Languages
Bootstrap DSP supports code snippets for:
- HTML
- React

Want more? Please open an issue in our [Github repo](https://github.com/foxbox-digital/bootstrap-dsp).


---

Built by the team at [Foxbox Digital](https://foxbox.com)
